<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white p-3 md:p-6"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <div class="space-y-6">
    <!-- Esercizio 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
    <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-2xl border-3 border-yellow-400">
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <%= imparare_tutti_badge(1) %>
        Osserva la Ruota della Gallina e completa la tabella a fianco: scrivi la probabilità che esca ogni numero elencato. Segui l'esempio.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-cyan-600 mb-2">LA RUOTA DELLA GALLINA</p>
          <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p262/p262_01.jpg", class: "max-w-full h-auto mx-auto", alt: "Ruota della Gallina" %>
        </div>

        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full border-collapse border border-cyan-400">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 bg-custom-blue-light text-center text-gray-800">Numero</th>
                <th class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 bg-custom-blue-light text-center text-gray-800">Casi favorevoli / Casi possibili</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">1</td>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-custom-blue-light">
                  <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: 3, den: 8 %>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">3</td>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">
                  <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: nil, den: 8, num_answer: "1" %>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">7</td>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">
                  <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: nil, den: 8, num_answer: "1" %>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">10</td>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">
                  <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: nil, den: 8, num_answer: "1" %>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">15</td>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">
                  <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: nil, den: 8, num_answer: "1" %>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">50</td>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">
                  <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: nil, den: 8, num_answer: "1" %>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">100</td>
                <td class="p-2 border border-cyan-400 text-center bg-white">
                  <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: nil, den: 8, num_answer: "0" %>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Esercizio 2 -->
    <div>
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <%= numero_esercizio_badge(2) %>
        Procurati un mazzo da 40 carte. Calcola in frazione e in percentuale quante probabilità hai, pescando a caso, di estrarre...
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-cyan-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">una figura:</span>
          <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: nil, den: 40, num_answer: "12" %>
          <span class="text-gray-700">=</span>
          <input type="text" data-correct-answer="0,3" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent">
          <span class="text-gray-700">=</span>
          <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: nil, den: 100, num_answer: "30" %>
          <span class="text-gray-700">=</span>
          <input type="text" data-correct-answer="30" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent">
          <span class="text-gray-700">%</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-cyan-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">una carta di denari:</span>
          <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: nil, den: 40, num_answer: "10" %>
          <span class="text-gray-700">=</span>
          <input type="text" data-correct-answer="0,25" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent">
          <span class="text-gray-700">=</span>
          <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: nil, den: 100, num_answer: "25" %>
          <span class="text-gray-700">=</span>
          <input type="text" data-correct-answer="25" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent">
          <span class="text-gray-700">%</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-cyan-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">una carta di valore minore o uguale a 5:</span>
          <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: nil, den: 40, num_answer: "20" %>
          <span class="text-gray-700">=</span>
          <input type="text" data-correct-answer="0,5" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent">
          <span class="text-gray-700">=</span>
          <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: nil, den: 100, num_answer: "50" %>
          <span class="text-gray-700">=</span>
          <input type="text" data-correct-answer="50" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent">
          <span class="text-gray-700">%</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-cyan-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">un asso:</span>
          <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: nil, den: 40, num_answer: "4" %>
          <span class="text-gray-700">=</span>
          <input type="text" data-correct-answer="0,1" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent">
          <span class="text-gray-700">=</span>
          <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: nil, den: 100, num_answer: "10" %>
          <span class="text-gray-700">=</span>
          <input type="text" data-correct-answer="10" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent">
          <span class="text-gray-700">%</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Esercizio 3 -->
    <div>
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <%= numero_esercizio_badge(3) %>
        Pensa al lancio di un dado a sei facce e indica con una X se le affermazioni sono vere (V) o false (F).
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-cyan-500">•</span> Un numero pari ha la stessa probabilità di uscire di uno dispari.</span>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <label class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-white border-2 border-cyan-500 rounded cursor-pointer hover:bg-custom-blue-light has-checked:bg-cyan-300">
              <input type="radio" name="vf1" class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer" data-correct-answer="true">
              <span>V</span>
            </label>
            <label class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-white border-2 border-cyan-500 rounded cursor-pointer hover:bg-custom-blue-light has-checked:bg-cyan-300">
              <input type="radio" name="vf1" class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer" data-correct-answer="false">
              <span>F</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-cyan-500">•</span> È certo che uscirà un numero da 1 a 6.</span>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <label class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-white border-2 border-cyan-500 rounded cursor-pointer hover:bg-custom-blue-light has-checked:bg-cyan-300">
              <input type="radio" name="vf2" class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer" data-correct-answer="true">
              <span>V</span>
            </label>
            <label class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-white border-2 border-cyan-500 rounded cursor-pointer hover:bg-custom-blue-light has-checked:bg-cyan-300">
              <input type="radio" name="vf2" class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer" data-correct-answer="false">
              <span>F</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-cyan-500">•</span> Il numero 1 ha maggior probabilità di uscire degli altri.</span>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <label class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-white border-2 border-cyan-500 rounded cursor-pointer hover:bg-custom-blue-light has-checked:bg-cyan-300">
              <input type="radio" name="vf3" class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer" data-correct-answer="false">
              <span>V</span>
            </label>
            <label class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-white border-2 border-cyan-500 rounded cursor-pointer hover:bg-custom-blue-light has-checked:bg-cyan-300">
              <input type="radio" name="vf3" class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer" data-correct-answer="true">
              <span>F</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-cyan-500">•</span> La probabilità che non esca un numero da 1 a 6 è dello 0%.</span>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <label class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-white border-2 border-cyan-500 rounded cursor-pointer hover:bg-custom-blue-light has-checked:bg-cyan-300">
              <input type="radio" name="vf4" class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer" data-correct-answer="true">
              <span>V</span>
            </label>
            <label class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-white border-2 border-cyan-500 rounded cursor-pointer hover:bg-custom-blue-light has-checked:bg-cyan-300">
              <input type="radio" name="vf4" class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer" data-correct-answer="false">
              <span>F</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
  </div>
</div>
